					</div>	
					<p class="text-sm">This box has no Common Vukkies.<br>Unique: Vukky Meat (Normal, Cooked, Burnt)</p>
				</div></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><div class="rounded-lg py-10 px-10 m-10 bg-gray-200 bg-opacity-30">
					<img class="max-h-48" src="./resources/pukkyvukkybox.webp"/>
					<div class="inline-flex justify-between">
						<p>Pukky Box<br>50</p> <button class="ml-10 button button-blue purchase" id="pukky" onclick="buyBox(this.id)">Buy</button>
					</div>	
