					<img class="max-h-48" src="./resources/beggarsvukkybox.webp"/>
					<div class="inline-flex justify-between">
						<p>Beggars Box<br>2.5</p> <button class="ml-10 button button-blue purchase" id="beggars" onclick="buyBox(this.id)">Buy</button>
					</div>	
					<p class="text-sm">This box consists of only commons and uncommons!<br>Beggars can't be choosers!</a><br>Unique: None, silly!</p>
